Na.

454
00:38:22,384 --> 00:38:23,385
Počkej.

455
00:38:24,219 --> 00:38:25,220
Hej.

456
00:38:26,263 --> 00:38:28,598
Sama to nevyhraješ.

457
00:38:31,018 --> 00:38:33,854
